# --- Adobe PDF Services API (for XFA form filling) ---
# Get credentials from: https://developer.adobe.com/document-services/docs/overview/pdf-services-api/
# Required for filling pure XFA/LiveCycle forms (e.g., IMM 1295)
# ADOBE_PDF_SERVICES_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id
# ADOBE_PDF_SERVICES_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret
